{
  "stem": "25912.6",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "But she arranged for me to go to [INAUDIBLE] grammar school, where there was a boys' school and a girls' school in the same building-- separate, but in the same building.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "And I must have been one of the early girls in a boys' school, because I had all my lessons with the boys.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "And I decided that I wanted to go to LSE.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And in January '49, I took what was known as the Leverhulme scholarship examination, which was an entrance for all London university colleges.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "And my first choice was LSE.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "My second choice was University College.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "And that consisted of an essay paper and a general knowledge paper.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "And imagine my surprise when I opened the examination paper for the essays, and the first essay subject was-- [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] my God.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] Something's a dreadful curse-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] foreign rule is a dreadful curse, and the minor benefits it can confer can never compensate for the spiritual degradation it involves.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I think the examiner was looking for an essay on colonialism.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It did not read like that to me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I wrote for three hours.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I never read it-- essay.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't know what the English was like.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "In any case, it got me a place both at University College and at LSE.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I started at LSE in October 1949, just after my 19th birthday, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] having had a strange education, to say the least.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I hadn't lost any time.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That's a great achievement.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Didn't stop me.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Very well.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "All the girls at school took a great interest in me, were very helpful, very friendly.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
